Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:24.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない夢を　君と君と　いつか　叶えられるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:31.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなれる　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:43.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,それはPreviousもなく出会う奇跡 Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:48.93,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,素顔を隠しながら　守るよ　もうひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:54.07,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,わかってるんだずっと　その孤独を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:59.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah...　恐れないで　迷わないで　ありのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:04.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,約束する　必ず迎えに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:10.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,届かない　明日は　高く高く　果てなく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:16.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,目の前にあるReal　願いこの空に消えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:22.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない　夢を　君が君が　いつか　ヒカリ望むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:27.88,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとたどり着く　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:33.45,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,君を　君を　君を　守りたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:37.81,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll Be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:24.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果將來能和你一起實現那永恆的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:31.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定能夠變強 現在就穿越時空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:43.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那是沒有預告的奇跡邂逅 是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:48.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上面具守護你 再也不會孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:54.07,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直明白你的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:59.43,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,啊..不要害怕 不要疑惑 做你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:04.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證 一定會去迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:10.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無法觸及的明天 高高在上無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:16.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的現實讓願望消散在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:22.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你在永恆的夢中期盼光明來臨的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:27.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定會到達那裏 現在就穿越時空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:33.45,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我想要守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:37.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我將與你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:16.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつまでもキミの夢も明日(あす)も未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:22.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなるよ Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:35.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,気持ちよダッシュして　どんなピンチも追い越せ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:41.06,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミを(きっと)すぐに(Soon you feel)もう安心だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:46.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,アイマイ弱いハート　限界超えの勇気は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:52.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも(今も)キミの(信号)キャッチ I am ready！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:56.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰よりキミが大事だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:23:03.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,熱くなってく　さあこの心で戦える！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:07.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミの夢も明日(あす)も未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:14.01,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,この手で絶対守るから　誓ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:18.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな涙も拭いてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.72,0:23:24.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,危なっかしいな　でも笑顔でまた困らせて？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:27.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　まだまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:30.02,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,小さな勇者は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.02,0:23:32.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　もっともっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:37.75,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,強くなる Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:16.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠守護你的夢想 你的明天 你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:22.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會變得更強大 幼獅雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:35.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,讓心情馳騁起來 超越各種危機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:41.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會馬上就讓你覺得安心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:46.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,曖昧弱小的心需要超越極限的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:52.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時都能捕捉到你的信號 我準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:56.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為比誰都在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:23:03.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,熱情不斷高漲 來吧 用這個心情去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:07.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你的夢想 你的明天 你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:14.01,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓一定用這雙手來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:18.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你拭去所有的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.72,0:23:24.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,看著好擔心啊 但是你的笑容又讓人不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:27.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為因為 還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:30.02,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.02,0:23:32.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為因為 要變得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:37.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,更強更強 幼獅雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長也真是愛整事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡服騎射麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種化石一樣古老的血脈..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也練得起勁呢 多爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 沒能經常來看你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 館長這種麻煩差事 根本不適合我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長是出色的館長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 很適合你呢 不愧是我特製的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我為你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為你嚮往的自己吧 多爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開 葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女人..把大妃..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的大妃..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃吧 葉太郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你殺她的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子小姐 由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我KnightLancer來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:03:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希露比亞..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太亂來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然傷成這樣 不過你很了不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面對四神的哈娜姐姐能戰成這樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不能再逞強了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去媽媽的..家人的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子小姐的包..還有槍袋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲醬 真緒大人和朱藤小姐她們..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個大洞是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想大概是依子小姐打破的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們可能一起從這個洞離開了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:04:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要老實待著才行啊 明明傷到腳了說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.35,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,這點小傷沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:08.37,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 乖乖聽姐姐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬 依子小姐 葉太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位善良溫柔的多爾袞先生..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然變得這麼暴烈..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是真的要殺我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 實在沒法進行反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多爾袞先生比我高了4個位階
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是第二階中位的力天使
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時也是館長的近衛 四神的首領
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最後一擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中世紀歐洲堪稱最強的全副武裝的騎士們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連他們都無力抗衡這個武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是..多爾袞先生的槍的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開 葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然用那個女人的槍？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便手持這把槍..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便手握珍惜之人的心意都阻擋不了他 我..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟還能使出這樣的力量..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能輸 在相信我的女士面前騎士..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能輸呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴著大妃的面具的我..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不可以輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了女士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻擋不了..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士..為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混小子..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 幫你製作面具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是為了讓你去做這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 多爾..是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓情同手足的你們彼此廝殺..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為我太著急了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你..這麼做到底是為了什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能呢..你..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長 別再勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要..休息一會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不但對朱藤小姐..竟然連你都想殺..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你以為失去了珍愛的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會彌補我的過錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算走掉了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對女孩子真是呵護有加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都在場麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是故意輸掉讓她去找依子的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是說過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用理會館長的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過希望能讓她和朱藤小姐打一場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士會為了重要的人變強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你覺得怎樣？是不是跟你預料的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我想的不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是先避一避比較好 在依子心情好起來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱藤小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才更讓人害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以現世騎士團 東亞區館館長孫大妃騎士之名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此封花房葉太郎為大騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你 葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜 葉太郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？為什麼突然就升格了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！不這樣做的話怎麼向依子賠禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就閉上嘴乖乖成為大騎士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這種理由..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 你可是和身為力天使的多爾打得不相上下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算封為大騎士也是低了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續堅強下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在對葉太郎先生做什麼下流之事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說下流之事是什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在澡堂給葉太郎犒勞一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要打嗎？好嘞 趕緊讓我報仇吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長 請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 你是站在誰那邊啊 多爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉..升格..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:16:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明不想當騎士了..可這樣反而越來越..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明小姐 哈娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的事情 真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這事已經沒關繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其實也想跟希露比她們道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為大家都有學業在身 所以館長放她們回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連那樣小的孩子都為了葉太郎君而來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎君 真是人氣十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒 那時候為什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就只有你留下來了麼 一直到依子小姐恢復為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 因為至今為止我一直受到依子小姐的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以至少在這種時候..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說 多爾那傢伙本來打算不再當騎士了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於自己想殺了你這件事似乎對他打擊很大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會..那是因為 我要去阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 別著急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們家的大嬸已經阻止他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說多爾不幹的話她也不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 多爾袞先生他..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論多爾還是你 你們男騎士真是太耿直了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明小姐最喜歡多爾袞先生了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是呢 畢竟是寶貴的四神戰友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有明小姐這樣的人在身邊 多爾袞先生一定也很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼珍惜同伴..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當騎士的男人真的都很遲鈍耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 反正那傢伙已經..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.75,0:17:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子這混蛋 下次我一定要報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手吧 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不能讓你太擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的事真的對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事已經說多少遍了..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來..「我的大妃」麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也變得能說會道了啊 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那是 那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊？愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在打掃房子啊 必須弄得乾乾淨淨才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被依子小姐以為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在她不在的時候懈怠了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬是不知者無罪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了 只顧你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來必須要做的是..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎大人他們馬上就要回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬 你到底是怎麼了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到家後一直..不 自從葉太郎大人不在之後..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得葉太郎是因為我才離開的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer..就是葉太郎吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 葉太郎君 朱藤小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的這段期間 家裏怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 那個..我已經盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼這種表情啊 大家都很擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不覺得內疚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這..這個..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 所以才說葉太郎沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:20:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒小姐說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後要比以前更加嚴格管教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒誒 等等..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還要等什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 所以說..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 朱藤小姐 至少今天..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今天開始就要嚴格鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:20.08,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎先生 這幾天訓練都落下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人..回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:21.89,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 真緒小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣再做30次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再高一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來下了一招蠢棋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下孫大妃暫時不可能對他出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此期間..我們非洲區館
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要登上現世騎士團的頂點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:09.96,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,525)}成為嚮往的自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 聽仔細
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「馬」這個字的形狀 是馬和馬互相扶持得來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:46.26,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.26,0:23:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬和馬..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要隨便亂教啊 沒看到這麼多筆劃都糾纏在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.30,0:23:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糾纏在一起什麼的 愛麗絲好色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.05,0:23:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才..才不色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說話說 愛麗絲真讓人不爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.72,0:23:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.54,0:23:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊 我們不是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.41,0:23:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是大發慈悲當你朋友而已 你別太得意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.97,0:24:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.51,0:24:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集的槍假面是久違的學校回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳也要去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.30,0:24:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 聽仔細
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫作「白姬」讀作「可愛」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你到底是老師還是學生啊
